{"title": "Where There's a Will (Dramatic Reading)", "description": "Minnie Waters has been running the Hope Spring health resort for many years with her father, Doctor Waters, when he suddenly passes away.  The ownership of Hope Springs hangs in the balance when the will states the Doctor\u2019s good-for-nothing grandson will inherit the resort but unfortunately, he is nowhere to be found.  Minnie must try to save the spa with the help of family, friends, and actors while adhering to the strict demands of the will.  While this book is not a typical Mary Roberts Rinehart mystery story, it is full of comedy, shenanigans, intrigue, and deception that is sure to keep readers entertained and wondering what will happen next! - Summary by Jenn Broda<br><br><b>Cast List:</b><br>\r\nMinnie Waters (narrator): <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/13140\">Jenn Broda</a><br>\r\nSam van Alstyne: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/16240\">HelloCentral</a><br>\r\nDoctor Waters: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/8425\">Larry Wilson</a><br>\r\nTillie: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/16999\">Krista Zaleski</a><br>\r\nPatty Jennings: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/13075\">Rita Boutros</a><br>\r\nMike: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/10542\">David Purdy</a><br>\r\nMr. Thoburn: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/6754\">ToddHW</a><br>\r\nSallie van Alstyne: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/17177\">MJ Rodriguez</a><br>\r\nAmanda King: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/16615\">Marie Christian</a><br>\r\nMiss Cobb: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/17098\">Carol Sutton</a><br>\r\nMrs. Biggs: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/13661\">Lynette Caulkins</a><br>\r\nSenator Biggs: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/16550\">Kerry Adams</a><br>\r\nThe Bishop: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/16205\">James R. Hedrick</a><br>\r\nMr. Jennings: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/12980\">Wayne Cooke</a><br>\r\nMrs. Moody: <a href=\"https://libriv